<h1>Reset your TFT Smart Hub password</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.display_name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your TFT Smart Hub account. If this was you, copy the code below or click the link to continue.</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 16px 0;">
  <code style="background:#f4f4f4; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;"><%= @reset_token %></code>
</p>

<p>You can also open the secure reset page with this button:</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background-color: #4361ee; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;">
    Reset my password
  </a>
</p>

<p>This link and code expire in 2 hours. If you didn’t request a reset, you can ignore this email — your password will stay the same.</p>

<p>— The TFT Smart Hub team</p>
